            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
                <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> consacré <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> par les Grecs.</p>
                <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> doubles <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> sur <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> les peuples <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <supplied reason="lost">dit</supplied> que tous <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <supplied reason="lost">ayant expédié</supplied> cent navires 
                <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> vous avez reçu en cadeau <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> des céréales <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>; les céréales inespérées <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> Grecs, vous êtes 
